data.description: This home has wonderful characteristics and charm. 3 bedrooms on second story, 2 baths, and a 4 car garage are some of which it has to offer (primary bedroom also has 3 closets)! Open floor plan, main floor laundry and multiple updates that include fresh paint inside and around outdoor window trim, newer carpet, high efficiency furnace, water heater, sump pump, shingles, windows, circuit breakers and stainless steel refrigerator. The oversized garage also has newer overhead doors with openers. Within walking distance of small businesses, parks/playgrounds, aquatic center and schools - don't miss your opportunity to see this home.
